name: The Night Walks of Versova, Mumbai
description: Every night, while I was staying in Versova, Mumbai, I used to look outside my window for sometime. I enjoyed sitting calmly and observing these orange-lit streets. Watching people roam without a worry in the world, strolling probably after a delicious meal they just had. The cool breeze paired with the rustling of the trees reminds me of the late night drives I used to go on with my family. | Resolution: 5959 x 3352 | Collection: Mundane Hues. |
